;Touring
* [[Shane Gibson (musician)|Shane Gibson]] - Guitar (2007<U+2013>2010) <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metalunderground.com/news/details.cfm?newsid=33246|title=Korn Touring Guitarist Situation Clarified|publisher=metal underground}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.shaneguitar.com/sg_bio.html |title=Shane Gibson Official Website |publisher=Shaneguitar.com |date= |accessdate=2011-02-24}}</ref>
