* [[Zac Baird]] &nbsp;<U+2013> keyboard, piano, backing vocals (2006<U+2013>present)<ref>[http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/news/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1003592846 Korn Goes Experimental, Vents Anger On New Album] Billboard.com Retrieved: 2009-04-03</ref>

